citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:30 - 11:00
on 19-NOV-18.
After ringing the doorbell and knocking on the door, calling the contact number (left message) and waiting for one
half hour, no responsible person was present to conduct an inspection.
